definition: essence/extract/vitality/energy/semen/sperm/mythical goblin spirit/highly perfected/elite/the pick of sth/proficient (refined ability)/extremely (fine)/selected rice (archaic)

sentences.english: Each file contains linear PCM essence.
sentences.chinese: 每個文件都包含有線性PCM精髓。

sentences.english: Protection of your vibratory essence is vital.
sentences.chinese: 至關重要的是保護你們的振動精髓。

sentences.english: It contains the whole gospel and the essence of the covenant of grace. It has been in great measure fulfilled.
sentences.chinese: 應許中涵蓋了全本的福音，也蘊藏著恩典之約的精髓。

sentences.english: Enterprise clarifies, cuts through, and captures, the essence of the evolutionary spirit.
sentences.chinese: 進取心可以釐清一切，披荊斬棘直搗演化的精髓。

sentences.english: There is one thing we can see with our eye, the architecture style of the blockhouse.
sentences.chinese: 我們能用眼睛看到的精髓之一就是碉樓的建築風格。

sentences.english: Impropriety is the soul of wit.
sentences.chinese: 不規矩是打趣話的精髓。

sentences.english: Gathering Ten Powerful Elements, which means free-dom, is the essence of the wheel of the time.
sentences.chinese: 南久旺丹，意爲十相自在，是時輪之精髓。

sentences.english: Intangible cultural context is the essence of heritage, making wood and stone worthy of our interest.
sentences.chinese: 無形文化環境是遺產的精髓，它使得木石有了意義。

sentences.english: A simple example will illustrate the essence of Smith’s idea.
sentences.chinese: 舉一個簡單的例子就能說清史密斯觀點的精髓。

sentences.english: That IS the essence of homeschooling and learning as a family.
sentences.chinese: 這就是家庭教育的精髓。

sentences.english: Now that you don't obtain the essence you certainly have no the function of Tao.
sentences.chinese: 你還未獲得道心精髓，當然完全不具備道行功能。

sentences.english: These are the core tenets of the “green economy”.
sentences.chinese: 而這些，是綠色經濟的核心精髓。

sentences.english: The color is the essence of design, and this is even truer in poster design.
sentences.chinese: 色彩是設計的精髓所在，在海報設計中尤爲如此。

sentences.english: Above-head resonating is called quintessence and key in bel conto singing.
sentences.chinese: 面罩共鳴被稱爲美聲唱法的精髓和關鍵。

sentences.english: To clear up this confusion, I will extract the essence of the concept of encodings.
sentences.chinese: 爲了消除這種誤解，我將總結編碼概念的精髓。

sentences.english: Suck out some marrow. That one was.
sentences.chinese: 要我說“吸取一些精髓”，那纔是話中有話。
